34Dwarf_P_Debug
35dwarf_producer_init(Dwarf_Unsigned flags, Dwarf_Callback_Func func,
36 Dwarf_Handler errhand, Dwarf_Ptr errarg, Dwarf_Error *error)
37{
38 Dwarf_P_Debug dbg;
39 int mode;
40
41 if (flags & DW_DLC_READ || flags & DW_DLC_RDWR) {
42 DWARF_SET_ERROR(NULL, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
43 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
44 }
45
46 if (flags & DW_DLC_WRITE)
47 mode = DW_DLC_WRITE;
48 else {
49 DWARF_SET_ERROR(NULL, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
50 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
51 }
52
53 if (func == NULL) {
54 DWARF_SET_ERROR(NULL, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
55 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
56 }
57
58 if (_dwarf_alloc(&dbg, DW_DLC_WRITE, error) != DW_DLE_NONE)
59 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
60
61 dbg->dbg_mode = mode;
62
63 if (_dwarf_init(dbg, flags, errhand, errarg, error) != DW_DLE_NONE) {
64 free(dbg);
65 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
66 }
67
68 dbg->dbgp_func = func;
69
70 return (dbg);
71}
72
73Dwarf_P_Debug
74dwarf_producer_init_b(Dwarf_Unsigned flags, Dwarf_Callback_Func_b func,
75 Dwarf_Handler errhand, Dwarf_Ptr errarg, Dwarf_Error *error)
76{
77 Dwarf_P_Debug dbg;
78 int mode;
79
80 if (flags & DW_DLC_READ || flags & DW_DLC_RDWR) {
81 DWARF_SET_ERROR(NULL, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
82 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
83 }
84
85 if (flags & DW_DLC_WRITE)
86 mode = DW_DLC_WRITE;
87 else {
88 DWARF_SET_ERROR(NULL, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
89 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
90 }
91
92 if (func == NULL) {
93 DWARF_SET_ERROR(NULL, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
94 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
95 }
96
97 if (_dwarf_alloc(&dbg, DW_DLC_WRITE, error) != DW_DLE_NONE)
98 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
99
100 dbg->dbg_mode = mode;
101
102 if (_dwarf_init(dbg, flags, errhand, errarg, error) != DW_DLE_NONE) {
103 free(dbg);
104 return (DW_DLV_BADADDR);
105 }
106
107 dbg->dbgp_func_b = func;
108
109 return (dbg);
110}
111
112int
113dwarf_producer_set_isa(Dwarf_P_Debug dbg, enum Dwarf_ISA isa,
114 Dwarf_Error *error)
115{
116
117 if (dbg == NULL || isa >= DW_ISA_MAX) {
118 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
119 return (DW_DLV_ERROR);
120 }
121
122 dbg->dbgp_isa = isa;
123
124 return (DW_DLV_OK);
125}
